title: Looking for jg Ranked team (ANY RANK)
body:
Hey guys,
The XxxNew World OrderxxX has had recent roster changes over the last few days and we are currently looking for a dedicated jungled for our semi-serious ranked team. We are accepting players of all ranks, add me IGN: Pandadude123

replies.body:
I rarely ever get jungle in ranked, would be nice to finally be able to jungle. You can test me if you want, I'm not the best ever, but I can always try, though if its a team that gets really toxic for a mistake or 2 I'm not interested then, but otherwise ill try it.
----
(Note: I am usually available from __7-9pm__ most weekday nights, I am also available about **80%** weekends)
